cps.api.request

  • Packages that use cps.api.request 
    Package Description
    cps.api.action  
    cps.api.request  
    cps.server  
    cps.server.controllers  
  • Classes in cps.api.request used by cps.api.action 
    Class and Description
    Request
    Base class for all client requests.
    RequestHandler
    Is used to implement request dispatching.
  • Classes in cps.api.request used by cps.api.request 
    Class and Description
    CancelOnetimeParkingRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to cancel their parking reservation.
    ComplaintRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to file a complaint.
    CustomerRequest
    Base class for client requests that represent customer actions.
    FullSubscriptionRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to purchase a full monthly subscription.
    IncidentalParkingRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to park right now, without making a reservation or buying a subscription.
    ListMyComplaintsRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to see a list of all the complaints that they have filed, and their status.
    ListOnetimeEntriesRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to see a list of all the onetime parking services that they have purchased (incidental parking or reservation), and their status.
    ListParkingLotsRequest
    Is sent by the client application when the application needs to display a list of parking lots to the user.
    LoginRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to login with their email and password that they received from previously buying a service.
    OnetimeParkingRequest
    Base class for one-time parking service requests: incidental parking (park now) or reserved parking.
    ParkingEntryRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer has a reservation or a subscription, and they want to park their car.
    ParkingExitRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to retrieve their car from the parking lot.
    RegularSubscriptionRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to purchase a regular monthly subscription.
    Request
    Base class for all client requests.
    RequestHandler
    Is used to implement request dispatching.
    ReservedParkingRequest
    Is sent by the client application when a customer wants to reserve parking for some point in the future.
    SubscriptionRequest
    Base class for monthly subscription purchase requests - full or regular.
